Choctaw County Schools Offering Meals to Students During COVID-19
The Choctaw County Child Nutrition Program will be issuing breakfast and lunch grab bags.
April 13th to May 18th
Monday, 
Wednesday, and Friday (10am-12pm)
Locations:
Choctaw Co Elementary - Drive Thru
Lisman Town Hall
Pennington Town Hall
Southern Choctaw Elementary - Drive Thru
Shady Grove Park
Melvin Fire Station
Children 18 and under are eligible. We ask that the child be present to receive food.
Dates and times are subject to change. Continue to check the district website and facebook page for updates.
